Space stations in general,

3
00:00:10,881 --> 00:00:16,538
because we have ISS, obviously,
but we also have Tiangong 1 of China.

4
00:00:16,538 --> 00:00:18,309
We'll mention that at the end.

5
00:00:19,152 --> 00:00:22,562
Since the Shuttle was retired
in the summer of 2011,

6
00:00:22,562 --> 00:00:25,264
the only way to get
to the International Space Station

7
00:00:25,264 --> 00:00:29,551
for astronauts and cosmonauts
is using the Russian Soyuz.

8
00:00:29,551 --> 00:00:34,368
And you see here, in Baikonur,
the Soyuz rocket

9
00:00:34,368 --> 00:00:37,711
